node.text:
Probably of the more challenging plants I own, but also one of my most favorite! #variegatedfiddleleaffig 🌱 
.
.
I find that the new leaves grow in beautifully, but older leaves eventually get patches of yellow discoloration. I haven’t quite figured out how to stop/prevent it. If you have experience with this and know how to fix it, please let me know 💚💚💚 #variegatedplants #variegata #fiddleleaffig #plantcare
